{"tid":538550,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"[Chrome] Lihkg, Whatsapp web自動登出","createTime":"2018-01-23T17:04:22.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-03T06:11:23.000Z","uid":75760,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"f8eabc7ae71e19a828ca05608d8cf95c1f274c94","tid":538550,"uid":75760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-23T17:04:22.000Z","msg":"小弟想問下關於用Google Chrome果時 Lihkg 同Whatsapp web會自動登出嘅問題<br />\n<br />\n原本都無呢個問題，但係一月頭開始，呢兩個網係熄機再開果時會自動登出（已經tick左保持登入呢啲option，自己有一部Desktop 同Macbook，兩部都有呢個問題），整到平時上黎睇連登每次都要登入一次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n想問下係唔係Google Chrome setting 出錯左？ 可以點樣set先可以每次開機都已經login左？ 唔該曬大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e493688406e2a8d7cc545002e58cb2231a6bb86","tid":538550,"uid":81818,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-23T17:08:41.000Z","msg":"係咪睇完咸網del history 呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有一欄係幫你 del埋 account password<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23d3f59f3e2ab9d4987cbd770a1084abd34e3783","tid":538550,"uid":75760,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-23T17:10:13.000Z","msg":"放啲靚仔靚女相比大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  希望大家可以教教我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.funnygifs.xyz/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/smily-dog-cute.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.funnygifs.xyz%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2015%2F09%2Fsmily-dog-cute.jpg&h=71c16f26&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://www.lovethispic.com/uploaded_images/53451-Cute-Dog.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.lovethispic.com%2Fuploaded_image